    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i haven't even bought that drink in months. it's not like i've been seeing it on TV or anything. it just... appears. and it's always the exact same font and the exact same shade of neon green. it feels way too deliberate than just \"stress\" or \"subconscious\" stuff. like they're actually beaming it into my brain. don't you think that's weird?",
